=H= Archive manipulation

=h= tar.gz

Create:     ‹tar cvzf name.tar.gz src_dir›
List:       ‹tar tvzf name.tar.gz›
Unpack:     ‹tar xvzf name.tar.gz -C dest_dir›

=h= zip

Create:     ‹zip name.zip -r src_dir›
List:       ‹unzip -l name.zip›
Unpack:     ‹unzip name.zip -d dest_dir›

=h= rar

Create:     ‹rar a -r name.rar src_dir›
List:       ‹unrar l›
Unpack:     ‹unrar x name.rar dest_dir›
